hole_6.original_tactic:
cases h₆ with
| inl h₆ => exact Or.inl h₆
| inr h₆ =>
  have h₇ : p ≠ 0 := by linarith
  have h₈ : p ≠ 1 := by
    intro h
    have h₉ := h₃.ne_one
    contradiction
  have h₉ : p ≥ 3 := by
    by_contra h
    interval_cases p <;> contradiction
  have h₁₀ : p = 3 ∨ p ≥ 5 := by omega
  cases h₁₀ with
  | inl h₁₀ => exact Or.inr (Or.inl h₁₀)
  | inr h₁₀ => exact Or.inr (Or.inr h₁₀)
